### From Deed To Domain Awaits

[!IMAGE](img/seal3.png,64,64)

Inspired by adventure, discover **NfNth**, the dApp powered by *geocache* and an *explorer's trade*.
<br/><br/>
Use an NFT **deed domain** to access a **domain** and build **artifact** to share and trade with others.

To purchase an NFT deed domain, go to either [OpenSea](https://opensea.io/ocurio).


<br/>
<a href="https://opensea.io/ocurio" title="Buy on OpenSea" target="_blank"><img style="margin-left:24px; width:220px; border-radius:5px; box-shadow: 0px 1px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/opensea-static/Logomark/Badge%20-%20Available%20On%20-%20Light.png" alt="Available on OpenSea" /></a>

Next, revisit **nfnth.com** and select the <i class="material-icons">account_balance_wallet</i> icon in the upper-right to get started.



<br/>
Please note that if the **NFT** is transferred to another wallet, access to edit the domain's content is transferred to the new owner.




