<br/>
*Use of nfnth.com requires a web3.js-compliant wallet, such as [MetaMask](https://metamask.io/download) and/or [CoinBase](https://wallet.coinbase.com/) to access a domain and build artifact.*

### Build Domain

[!IMAGE](img/seal3.png,64,64)

Post content to build your domain. Posted content can consist of text, images, location, and datetimes.
<br/><br/>
Domain posts can only be added/edited/deleted by the owner of the NFT **deed domain**.

All posted content is public and can be viewed by anyone.

<br/>
Please note if the **NFT** is transferred to another wallet, both domain access and domain content are transferred to the new owner.
